00:21:44.429 --> 00:21:50.529
is let users start reading the comic book
before they made a purchase. And once a sure

00:21:50.529 --> 00:21:54.940
starts enjoying it, starts getting hooked,
that's when you give them the option to actually

00:21:54.940 --> 00:22:01.940
make a purchase within there.
It's now possible with our API. And it's really

00:22:01.990 --> 00:22:07.899
simple. With a single click, the user can
initiate the purchase, and with another click,

00:22:07.899 --> 00:22:12.080
complete and go back to reading the comic
book they were originally enjoying.

00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:15.259
That's it. That's all it takes for a user
to make a purchase within the application.

00:22:15.259 --> 00:22:22.169
Let me show you how it works.
Just like we wanted to make it really easy

00:22:22.169 --> 00:22:27.250
for users to make knows purchases, we also
wanted to make it stunningly simple for developers

00:22:27.250 --> 00:22:31.750
to implement it.
All it takes for you to implement this is

00:22:31.750 --> 00:22:37.000
a single line of code. There's one line of
code that integrates it and lets initiate

00:22:37.000 --> 00:22:41.379
the purchase flow where the users can go make
a purchase. And once the purchase is complete,

00:22:41.379 --> 00:22:45.370
you get a call back that you can take a new
application and deliver the goods with a single

00:22:45.370 --> 00:22:49.289
line of code.
That's all it is.

00:22:49.289 --> 00:22:52.350
And the session later today we will talk about
this platform and API in a lot more detail

00:22:52.350 --> 00:22:56.200
