00:22:56.200 --> 00:23:00.909
There's one more thing. We wanted to make
it simple for users, we wanted to make it

00:23:00.909 --> 00:23:05.570
simple for developers to implement it, but
we also wanted to figure out, how do we price

00:23:05.570 --> 00:23:09.669
it so that all of you can build amazing businesses
on this platform.

00:23:09.669 --> 00:23:16.309
When we looked around, we found that applications
tend to pay very complicated set of fees.

00:23:16.309 --> 00:23:21.179
There are setup fees, there are minimum fees,
there are monthly fees, there are fixed fees.

00:23:21.179 --> 00:23:27.360
We wanted to keep it simple.
We also found out that online applications

00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:32.090
